中華人民共和國是世界最大棉花消费国、第二大棉花生产国。[[新疆|新疆]]是[[中国棉业|中国大陆棉花]]的主要产地，截至2020年，当地[[棉花|棉花]]产量已经占到中華人民共和國全国产量的87%，世界棉花產量的20%<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%87%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E7%BB%B4%E6%97%8F%E9%81%AD%E5%89%A5%E5%89%8A%E6%B2%A6%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%A5%B4%E9%9A%B6/a-55954153 |title=报告：五十多万新疆维族遭剥削沦「现代奴隶」 |accessdate=2021-03-28 |archive-date=2021-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327165053/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E4%BA%94%E5%8D%81%E5%A4%9A%E4%B8%87%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E7%BB%B4%E6%97%8F%E9%81%AD%E5%89%A5%E5%89%8A%E6%B2%A6%E7%8E%B0%E4%BB%A3%E5%A5%B4%E9%9A%B6/a-55954153 |dead-url=no |publisher=德國之聲中文網|language=zh}}</ref>，机採棉种植面积占棉花播种总面积的69.83%<ref>{{cite web |title=【数·百年】世界棉花看中国 中国棉花看新疆 |url=http://www.xinhuanet.com/video/sjxw/2021-03/25/c_1211083587.htm |website=新华社 |accessdate=2021-03-27 |date=2021-03-25 |archive-date=2021-03-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210328044155/http://www.xinhuanet.com/video/sjxw/2021-03/25/c_1211083587.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。每年秋季棉花进入采摘期，新疆铁路部门会开行棉花专列，方便内陆地区省份的摘棉工进入新疆採收<ref>{{cite web |title=新疆铁路部门开行87列专列方便摘棉工进疆 |url=http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2018-09/15/content_5322263.htm |website=中国政府网 |accessdate=2021-03-27 |date=2018-09-15 |archive-date=2020-12-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201215165232/http://www.gov.cn/xinwen/2018-09/15/content_5322263.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>。而新疆生产建设兵团的机採棉业务始于1996年，当时主要使用美制[[约翰迪尔|约翰迪尔]]及{{link-en|凯斯万国|Case IH|凯斯}}两个品牌的{{link-en|採棉机|Cotton picker}}<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sohu.com/a/209264073_617220|title=采棉机除了约翰迪尔和凯斯的进口产品，国产的到底能不能用？|publisher=农机通|date=2017-12-08|accessdate=2021-03-28|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513152143/https://www.sohu.com/a/209264073_617220|dead-url=no}}</ref>，2018年起中国大陆本土品牌採棉机开始在新疆运用<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.sohu.com/a/308657868_617220|title=钵施然，用实力证明中国人可以干采棉机|publisher=农机通|date=2019-04-17|accessdate=2021-03-28|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513152127/https://www.sohu.com/a/308657868_617220|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2019年7月，澳广ABC调查节目《四角方圆》称，维吾尔族穆斯林被抓捕并被强迫在新疆的纺织厂工作。随後[[Cotton_On|Cotton On]]集团和Target澳大利亚公司对其供应链的内部展開调查，並宣布不再使用其新疆分包商采购的棉花<ref>{{cite news |title=“拒绝新疆棉花”源于澳洲，为什么“中刀”的是H&M？ |url=https://www.sbs.com.au/chinese/mandarin/zh-hans/say-no-to-xinjiang-cotton-originated-in-australia-but-why-is-h-m-boyctted |accessdate=2021-03-30 |archive-date=2021-05-13 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513152137/https://www.sbs.com.au/chinese/mandarin/zh-hans/say-no-to-xinjiang-cotton-originated-in-australia-but-why-is-h-m-boyctted |dead-url=no |publisher=SBS中文|language=zh}}</ref>。

2020年3月1日，[[澳大利亚战略政策研究所|澳大利亚战略政策研究所]]（{{lang-en|Australian Strategic Policy Institute, ASPI}}）发布一份研究报告<ref>{{Cite web|title=Uyghurs for sale|url=https://www.aspi.org.au/report/uyghurs-sale|accessdate=2021-03-26|date=2020-03-01|publisher=Australian Strategic Policy Institute|language=en|archive-date=2020-08-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200824215335/https://www.aspi.org.au/report/uyghurs-sale|dead-url=no}}</ref>，称包括[[蘋果公司|苹果]]、[[耐克|耐克]]、[[阿迪达斯|阿迪达斯]] 、[[优衣库|优衣库]]和[[斯凯奇|斯凯奇]]在内的约83个知名消费品牌都有供应商与中国大陆维吾尔族及其他少数民族的强迫劳动有关，成千上万的维族人被强迫迁移到中国大陆各地工作。 <ref>{{Cite web|title=苹果、耐克等大公司卷入中国穆斯林强迫劳动丑闻|url=https://www.abc.net.au/chinese/2020-03-06/aspi-uyghur-china-forced-labour-report/12023986|accessdate=2021-03-26|author=Max Walden|date=2020-03-06|publisher=ABC中文|language=zh-cn|archive-date=2020-03-15|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200315192251/https://www.abc.net.au/chinese/2020-03-06/aspi-uyghur-china-forced-labour-report/12023986|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=名为“援疆”实为“劳动” 北京: 报告毫无事实根据|url=https://www.dw.com/zh/a-52602404|accessdate=2021-03-26|author=William Yang|date=2020-03-03|publisher=德国之声|language=zh-cn|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513152130/https://www.dw.com/zh/%E5%90%8D%E4%B8%BA%E6%8F%B4%E7%96%86%E5%AE%9E%E4%B8%BA%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8-%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC-%E6%8A%A5%E5%91%8A%E6%AF%AB%E6%97%A0%E4%BA%8B%E5%AE%9E%E6%A0%B9%E6%8D%AE/a-52602404|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2020年3月下旬，[[良好棉花发展协会|良好棉花发展协会]]（BCI）宣布在即将到来的棉花季暂停在新疆地区的工作，暂停在新疆发放良好棉花许可证，原因是持续存在关于该地区强迫劳动的报道和指控，并委托专家对新疆的情况进行外部评估，但會将在整个棉花季期间支持农民。<ref>{{Cite web|title=BCI pulls out of Xinjiang|url=https://www.ecotextile.com/2020032725887/materials-production-news/bci-pulls-out-of-xinjiang.html|accessdate=2021-03-27|author=Chris Remington|date=2020-03-27|publisher=Ecotextile News|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327144821/https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache%3AMJIDWDenhG4J%3Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ecotextile.com%2F2020032725887%2Fmaterials-production-news%2Fbci-pulls-out-of-xinjiang.html+&cd=1&hl=en&ct=clnk&gl=us&client=firefox-b-d|archivedate=2021-03-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref>10月21日，BCI决定停止在新疆的所有实地活动。<ref>{{Cite web|title=Better Cotton Initiative pulls out of Xinjiang|url=https://www.ecotextile.com/2020102226892/materials-production-news/better-cotton-initiative-pulls-out-of-xinjiang.html|accessdate=2021-03-28|author=Simon Glover|date=2020-10-22|publisher=Ecotextile News|language=en|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327171353/https://webcache.googleusercontent.com/search?q=cache%3A87r-ncUy9r0J%3Ahttps%3A%2F%2Fwww.ecotextile.com%2F2020102226892%2Fmaterials-production-news%2Fbetter-cotton-initiative-pulls-out-of-xinjiang.html+&cd=6&hl=en&ct=clnk&gl=us&client=firefox-b-d|archivedate=2021-03-27|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|title=Xinjiang Uyghur Autonomous Region (XUAR) Update|url=https://bettercotton.org/where-is-better-cotton-grown/china/announcement-bci-suspends-licensing-in-western-china/|accessdate=2021-03-26|date=2020-10-21|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20201107135536/https://bettercotton.org/where-is-better-cotton-grown/china/announcement-bci-suspends-licensing-in-western-china/|archivedate=2020-11-07|website=Better Cotton Initiative|dead-url=yes}}</ref>

2020年9月9日，[[彭博新聞社|彭博社]]援引发言人消息，称[[H&M|H&M]]没有与新疆地区的任何服装厂合作，目前没有从该地区采购任何产品，并表示已经采取措施确保中国大陆的供应商没有通过迁移计划雇用新疆工人。<ref>{{Cite web|title=H&M Says It’s Not Working With Any Garment Factories in Xinjiang|url=https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2020-09-09/h-m-says-it-s-not-working-with-any-garment-factories-in-xinjiang|accessdate=2021-03-27|author=Anton Wilen|date=2020-09-09|publisher=Bloomberg|language=en|archive-date=2021-05-13|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210513152138/https://www.bloomberg.com/tosv2.html?vid=&uuid=e9633470-b3fe-11eb-b24b-5bb33f86545a&url=L25ld3MvYXJ0aWNsZXMvMjAyMC0wOS0wOS9oLW0tc2F5cy1pdC1zLW5vdC13b3JraW5nLXdpdGgtYW55LWdhcm1lbnQtZmFjdG9yaWVzLWluLXhpbmppYW5n|dead-url=no}}</ref>9月16日，H&M宣布终止与中国大陆一间纱线供应商（华孚时尚）的关系，原因是该厂产品涉嫌用新疆少数族裔「强迫劳动」生产。<ref>{{Cite web|title=中国供应商涉新疆强迫劳动 H&M砍合作关系|url=https://www.swissinfo.ch/chi/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BE%9B%E5%BA%94%E5%95%86%E6%B6%89%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E5%BC%BA%E8%BF%AB%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8-h-m%E7%A0%8D%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB/46036842|accessdate=2021-03-27|author=瑞士资讯SWI|date=2020-09-16|agency=法新社|language=zh-cn|archive-date=2021-03-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210326182418/https://www.swissinfo.ch/chi/%E4%B8%AD%E5%9B%BD%E4%BE%9B%E5%BA%94%E5%95%86%E6%B6%89%E6%96%B0%E7%96%86%E5%BC%BA%E8%BF%AB%E5%8A%B3%E5%8A%A8-h-m%E7%A0%8D%E5%90%88%E4%BD%9C%E5%85%B3%E7%B3%BB/46036842|dead-url=no}}</ref>在发布的声明中<ref name="#1">{{Cite web|title=H&M Group statement on due diligence|url=https://hmgroup.com/sustainability/fair-and-equal/human-rights/h-m-group-statement-on-due-diligence/|accessdate=2021-03-24|author=H&M Group|date=2020-10|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-29|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210329035337/https://hmgroup.com/sustainability/fair-and-equal/human-rights/h-m-group-statement-on-due-diligence/|dead-url=no}}</ref>，H&M表示该公司对“新疆维吾尔自治区的强迫劳动和歧视少数民族”的相关报道“深表关切”，强调“不与位于新疆的任何服装制造工厂合作，也不从该地区采购产品或原材料”。<ref>{{Cite web|title=H&M to end ‘indirect’ relationship with Chinese supplier amid ‘forced labour’ allegations|url=https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/hm-china-forced-labour-huafu-fashion-co-cotton-xinjiang-b453138.html|accessdate=2021-03-27|author=Sabrina Barr|date=2020-09-16|publisher=The Independent|language=en|archive-date=2021-03-27|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210327025847/https://www.independent.co.uk/life-style/fashion/hm-china-forced-labour-huafu-fashion-co-cotton-xinjiang-b453138.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>

